com.google.template.soy.jssrc.restricted

Class JsExpr

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.template.soy.internal.targetexpr.TargetExpr
      • com.google.template.soy.jssrc.restricted.JsExpr

  • public final class JsExpr
extends TargetExpr
    Value class to represent a JS expression. Includes the text of the expression as well as the precedence of the top-most operator.

    Important: This class may only be used in implementing plugins (e.g. functions, directives).

    Note that while all behavior of JsExpr matches TargetExpr, the class serves to differentiate between languages and retain plugin behavior.
